page.title: 11Changes Since 1945.
page.content: Has the river changed since 1945? Yes - new quays have been built and the river has been deepened. More ships use the river. Has the district changed much? Yes- Glaxo Chemical Factory has come and many new homes built. Was your childhood different from todays childhood? Not much except that most people have more money. Is the fishing method of 1945 the same as todays? In 1945 it was mainly line fishing but in 1985 it's mainly net fishing. Has the school work changed? It has changed greatly. There is more variety of subjects and no more corporal punishments.
